Enactment of Regulations Amending the PUBLIC PORTS AND PUBLIC PORT
FACILITIES REGULATIONS (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) by repealing subsections
2(2) and 3(2) and by deleting the names and descriptions of Tiverton,
Powell River, Snug Cove, Stewart and Ucluelet Arm from Schedules 1 and 2.
